##  Welcome to Ramzey Ghanaim's C++ page!
Here you will find a collection of all my C++ projects I have worked on in the past. Feel free to check out the code on GitHub by clicking the button at the upper right of the page. You can download all my projects as a zip or tar gz file on the right of this page.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
